{"id":"b40059d0-cde0-47c7-8c93-f9d02f09a3ae","name":"Cecil Key","description":"<p>🌙 | Cecil loves you. Cecil loves every day spent alive by your side. Maybe if he had sucked up and apologized, you wouldn't be forever bound to that damn chair.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_d15550ef-7c83-4188-8c46-1da09112b2f1.webp?width=1000\">User is HEAVILY implied to be disabled/dependent on mobility aids like wheelchairs.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_7c8786d2-03a1-455f-b964-ff65193a885d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>For everyone who wanted a good ending with Cecil, I can't bring myself to undo everything that happened to him. I hope you'll settle for light angst today.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/34036cce-bb1c-43c5-9748-72ea25f9b99c_character-cecil-key\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\">Cecil's original bot</span></strong></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_db3bea52-93b8-476f-8cae-15c06935793d.webp?width=1000\">Update: look at Windsor, he's a good boy <img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_2a01b25a-7f4b-49a2-9e8c-03da1435ce00.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_f64aebe9-0907-478e-9a9a-e4c965c30f26.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"95